{"tid":2439422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日用拜車公例子，講比想打科興朋友聽，佢終於明白","createTime":"2021-03-09T08:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:22:03.000Z","uid":156652,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25ac739f5932693dd54c35dca6f1550e916ffbe8","tid":2439422,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"朋友：專家話幾單打針出事唔關科興事<br />\n我：咁當你好想中六合彩，星期一去拜車公，話想中六合彩，之後你兩日後當日買六合彩就就中左，咁你覺得同車公有冇直接關係？<br />\n朋友：緊係有啦！<br />\n我：咪係囉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6f103f4599ff98e68cd439dc7f45937e6281d7","tid":2439422,"uid":286155,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"你地覺得<br />\n樓主同佢個fd<br />\n邊個on9啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622fd83ebbcfa3a2513c10a1452d5fe71418813e","tid":2439422,"uid":392073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"我自己就咁諗 <br />\n假設政府講真 一日有一百幾十人會猝死又盛<br />\n而枝針又咁多人想打 之前好難排到<br />\n個死者又好驚有病 好注重健康要去打針<br />\n而咁岩打到個班人 咁岩有幾個人就過兩日猝死又病發<br />\n唔係直接關係 都有神秘不可抗力又超自然力量啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車公個風車 無事轉左會死 邊個會無事去轉呢"},{"pid":"3d119af9459da2f6638d1a96bf05234911c6e86d","tid":2439422,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d089965f97c048f33fe3ae308655e423678204e","tid":2439422,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925c2cf40d1f52a33ae440d4fcd8abaa4ff61af3","tid":2439422,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"又話長者病患易中武肺<br />\n<br />\n又叫長者自己衡量打唔打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a6b81f43587f821640c3ce86b9af67212e5f36","tid":2439422,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123cf0c57c56ea66dc1acd3136e64f1d253a1dc8","tid":2439422,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9db3088665463450d92edd8dba0bd0335bcf01f","tid":2439422,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f6f103f4599ff98e68cd439dc7f45937e6281d7","tid":2439422,"uid":286155,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"你地覺得<br />\n樓主同佢個fd<br />\n邊個on9啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"兩個都咁on9，當打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}